<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-11T12:20:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-11T12:20:00-05:00" n="583" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d583">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">761.94/7–2145: Telegram</note>
                                <head>No. 583<lb/><hi rend="italic">The Japanese Minister of Foreign
                                        Affairs</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_TS2" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Togo</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                        the Japanese Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_TS2" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Togo</hi></persName>)</head>
                                <opener>
                                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                                </opener>
                                <opener>
                                    <seg rendition="#left">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">very secret</hi>
                                        <lb/>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">urgent</hi>
                                    </seg>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-12T02:20:00+09:00">July 12, 1945—2:20
                                            a.m.</date> [<hi rend="italic">sic</hi>]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>894. Re my telegram No. 893.<note n="1" xml:id="d583fn1">
                                        <ref target="#d582">Document No. 582</ref>.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>When you convey this matter to them, please make it understood
                                    that the subject should be treated as absolutely secret. I
                                    realize that I am being presumptuous in saying this; I mention
                                    it merely to be sure.</p>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>